reviewText: not only are the women spectacular the real gem here is jason saints the referee. under 500 fights reffed he makes the perfect middle man for these women slinging it out

Boxing Babes If you have a 3D Television at home you must have this new 3D movie. This is for adults only. While your watching your favorite sports take a break and enjoy the cinematography in this film. If you love boxing you'll love this movie! If you love competition it's a must have. It's a fantastic addition to my new 3D collection. Looking forward to more releases.
